snippet.title: Amber Heard Admitting To Abusing Johnny Depp, Weinstein Update, #MakeSpaceForWomen | HBR News 241
snippet.description:
Join us on the HBR News show as we talk about the news of the week, from a huge bit of evidence regarding the Johnny Depp/Amber Heard domestic violence accusations, a testimony from one of Harvey Weinstein's accusers regarding his "privates", a couple of new woke hashtags that were making the rounds this weekend, a new piece of software that searches through your social media for problematic trends so that potential employers can decide whether or not to hire you, and more! Tune in @6pm Eastern!
